Title:
Being PLATINUM members of the Sky Team we had the best extra leg room seats (row 11) in Economy Class. Preferred to take these seats as the flying time was barely over 3 hours.

Kenya Airways needs to improve on the following:

1] Unlike KLM we were never addressed by name;
2] The movie screen was loose and kept falling down;
3] The beef curry was terrible (half raw). The chicken curry and fish options we took on later fights were better options;
4] Crew barely smiled. Looked like they make the same trip twice a day;
5] Overhead baggage’s sometimes get full even above the passengers’ seats. It is highly inconvenient to keep bags in other places on the aircraft.

The flight was generally comfortable and my hats off to the pilots for steering the otherwise nice aircraft well. Landing was perfect.

M. Daya
Platinum Member

